{"tid":1312231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天橋事件求助&執到個耳機","createTime":"2019-07-13T12:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T11:39:28.000Z","uid":263452,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e3a337d0472f67234a7b9b4397ab83d0d3ee1604","tid":1312231,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:56:58.000Z","msg":"今日5點前後<br />\n一個肥佬打完人比狗護送上天橋後比我地圍<br />\n我走出外圍後有另一班狗趕到<br />\n我係其中一個便衣狗正前方<br />\n我後面一堆人無路退佢仲叫我唔好擋住佢<br />\n之後用前臂頂係我條頸度同時搶左我口罩<br />\n後面d人又頂住我令我透唔到氣<br />\n野都講唔到<br />\n仲要繼續兇我<br />\n過幾秒佢鬆手後我企都無力企<br />\nd人見我無口罩拉左我去後面望唔到佢no.<br />\n想知有無人係live有望到or有拍片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n投訴佢一定無用<br />\n所以有無人知有咩法援可以直接出律師信比佢<br />\n學生哥窮到物資都買唔起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但好似用左for比人拉左既人打官司d錢好似對佢地唔住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw當時現場執到個耳機<br />\ntg同我講番係咩耳機我出黎比番你<br />\ntg:@fffwill"},{"pid":"07c6d9d7cc0dc89f8887b91de0c24a60fe375a23","tid":1312231,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:20:56.000Z","msg":"有無人可以同我講點做好...."},{"pid":"b35e63e427b3a944bf3baaec260726d067215ca7","tid":1312231,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5487a582c8bb707ed63310f9fe90ea5be94ac6","tid":1312231,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:32:28.000Z","msg":"你地係咪淨睇熱門?"},{"pid":"b98ed4dba38a882f08198bb0b6024f5cd903fdef","tid":1312231,"uid":69177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d49d181c17647a60b94d68c697e765b97b93c9","tid":1312231,"uid":258340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c